steps to compile ffmpeg for android to use with swarm control app

be sure to have the NDK defined in PATH in your bashrc file:

	NDK=/path/to/your/ndk/location    
	export PATH=$PATH:$NDK

1. Extract ffmpeg-1.0.7z here
2. Execute the script ffmpeg-1.0/build.sh
3. Call ndk-build APP_PLATFORM=android-8
